Residents of Mercy Njeri estate in Nakuru yesterday blocked the Nakuru-Kabarak road to protest the killing of two brothers by a police officer. Charles Kariuki and John Maina were shot dead by a CID officer commonly known as &lsquo;Kiarie&rsquo; after an argument with a bar owner who referred to them as thieves. &nbsp;Rongai OCPD Joseph Mwamburi claims the two were thugs who tried to break into a mobile money transfer service shop. Police are conducting investigations to ascertain the claims.&nbsp;